"measured input frequency as a fractional value with three digit decimal "
"precision (millihertz). Value of (DPLL_A_PIN_MEASURED_FREQUENCY / "
"DPLL_PIN_MEASURED_FREQUENCY_DIVIDER) is an integer part of a measured "
"frequency value. Value of (DPLL_A_PIN_MEASURED_FREQUENCY % "
"DPLL_PIN_MEASURED_FREQUENCY_DIVIDER) is a fractional part of a measured "
"frequency value."
msgstr ""

