"into its base frequency signal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../netlink/specs/dpll.yaml:451
msgid "esync-pulse (``u32``)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../netlink/specs/dpll.yaml:451
msgid ""
"A ratio of high to low state of a SYNC signal pulse embedded into base clock "
"frequency. Value is in percents."
msgstr ""

